lesson icon="fa fa-pencil" title="A Soft Introduction to Fragments" meta="Practice" meta_icon="fa fa-code"]This video demonstrates a use of a powerful Android feature - Fragments. We create a reusable login form that enables us to have different layouts on phones and tablet devices.[/stm_course_lesson][stm_course_lesson icon="fa fa-pencil" title="Communicating with Fragments " meta="Practice" meta_icon="fa fa-qrcode"]This video continues the previous one by showing a common and very powerful technique that allows a fragment to communicate with the activity that it is attached to.[/stm_course_lesson][stm_course_lesson icon="fa-icon-stm_icon_brain" badge="quiz" title="Testing your app" meta="Test" meta_icon="fa fa-check"]In this lesson, we will test your app in native environment[/stm_course_lesson][/stm_course_lessons][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Introduction to Mobile Apps Development', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis vestibulum turpis eu nunc volutpat vestibulum. Donec scelerisque arcu ac ante.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'developing-mobile-apps', '', '', '2015-08-05 06:17:26', '2015-08-05 06:17:26', '', 0, 'http://masterstudy.stylemixthemes.com/demo/?post_type=product&#038;p=486', 0, 'product', '', 2),
(488, 1, '2015-06-08 07:47:17', '2015-06-08 07:47:17', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_message message_box_style="solid-icon" message_box_color="peacoc" icon_fontawesome="fa fa-camera-retro"]A to Z guide to becoming a professional photographer - know how to properly use a camera and apply composition concepts.[/vc_message][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Have you always had a passion for taking pictures and thought about getting the proper photography training?</h3>\r\nPhotography is much more than simply taking a photo with your camera. There is a lot of technique and knowledge you need to know to perfectly capture moments.\r\n\r\nThis beginner course on photography will walk you through step by step every aspect you need to know to start improving your photography skills and potentially have your own photography business.\r\n\r\nIngred Shine has been a professional photographer and photography teacher for over 22 years. She''ll serve as your guide through improving your photography skills.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs][vc_tta_section title="Course Targets" tab_id="1436938259973-a86e9735-a51c"][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Basics of Cameras</li>\r\n	<li>Basics of Photography</li>\r\n	<li>Point and Shoot Cameras</li>\r\n	<li>Retouring Pictures on the Camera</li>\r\n	<li>Image Size and Resolution</li>\r\n	<li>DSLR Cameras</li>\r\n	<li>How to Properly Take a Picture</li>\r\n	<li>White Balance and Noise</li>\r\n	<li>Camera Menu and Settings</li>\r\n	<li>Retouring, Exposure and More</li>\r\n	<li>iPhone Cameras</li>\r\n	<li>Focus, Brightness, Flash and Filters</li>\r\n	<li>The Exposure Triangle â Aperature, Shutter and ISO</li>\r\n	<li>Manual Shooting</li>\r\n	<li>Shooting Techniques and Lenses</li>\r\n	<li>Framing and Posing</li>\r\n	<li>Objects of Interest and Perspective</li>\r\n	<li>Rule of Thirds</li>\r\n	<li>Depth of Field</li>\r\n	<li>Lighting and Time of Day</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section