s.com/demo/?post_type=product&#038;p=488', 0, 'product', '', 1),
(490, 1, '2015-06-05 07:47:59', '2015-06-05 07:47:59', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 class="tab-title">Course Description</h3>\r\n<div class="js-simple-collapse" data-more="Full details">\r\n<div class="js-simple-collapse-inner">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Over 23,000 satisfied students enrolled in my courses</li>\r\n	<li>Featured as one of the Best courses on Udemy</li>\r\n	<li>Overall, 380+ TOP Reviews from very happy students</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis course will dramatically increase your level of Productivity. It is comprised of solid mindset strategies, but it will also equip you with proven techniques and simple methods that will boost your Productivity and help you Get Things Done in a very short period of time.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][stm_multy_separator css=".vc_custom_1436961961162{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 17px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1436961911928{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"]\r\n<p class="lead">Daylight Saving Time (DST) is a way of making better use of the natural daylight by setting your clock forward one hour during the summer months, and back again in the fall.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][stm_multy_separator css=".vc_custom_1436961967112{margin-top: 17px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="Curriculum" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1436962357437{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"][stm_course_lessons title="Section 1: Introduction to Productivity"][stm_course_lesson icon="fa fa-youtube-play" badge="preview" title="Introduction to the course" meta="03:50"]Intro video for the entire course.[/stm_course_lesson][stm_course_lesson icon="fa fa-youtube-play" badge="preview" title="Everyone Can Be Productive" meta="03:23"]Have you ever said to yourself: "I simply don''t have the productivity gene!"\r\nWell, here''s why you are wrong:)[/stm_course_lesson][/stm_course_lessons][stm_course_lessons title="Section 2: Goal Setting"][stm_course_lesson icon="fa fa-youtube-play" badge="preview" title="The Game Changer " meta="02:03"]Why setting goals can be a game changer?[/stm_course_lesson][stm_course_lesson icon="fa fa-youtube-play" badge="preview" title="``Unrealistic``, Exciting Goals"]Why your goals NEED to be exciting.[/stm_course_lesson][stm_course_lesson icon="fa fa-youtube-play" badge="preview" title="Goal Setting - Accountability "]Most people don''t achieve their goals, because they don''t follow through. They simply give up. Be different!\r\n\r\nYour goals need to:\r\n1) be specific\r\n2) have a deadline\r\n3) make you accountable\r\n\r\n"accountable"? what does it mean?\r\nShare your goals with other people and make them keep you accountable. Thanks to this approach you will start associating a lot of pain with not achieving your goals. It can tenfold your chances of success. Watch this video about powerful goal setting and learn why[/stm_course_lesson][/stm_course_lessons][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Basic Time Management Course', 'Personal time management skills are essential for professional &amp; personal success in any area of life. Those able to successfully implement time management strategies are able to control their workload rather than spend each day in a frenzy of activity reacting to crisis after crisis.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'basic-time-management-course', '', '', '2015-08-05 06:18:06', '2015-08-05 06:18:06', '', 0, 'http://masterstudy.stylemixthemes.com/demo/?post_type=product&#038;p=490', 0, 'product', '', 1),
