amming for both beginners and Intermediate developers.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'swift-programming-for-beginners', '', '', '2015-08-05 06:18:29', '2015-08-05 06:18:29', '', 0, 'http://masterstudy.stylemixthemes.com/demo/?post_type=product&#038;p=525', 0, 'product', '', 2),
